  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Claudia, a woman who has lost her job as a reporter, decides to go to investigate the psychiatric hospital \"Milagros\" which keeps a story as secret as it is macabre. During this journey she meets people who have the same intentions and others who will get in the way.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With the help of her new companions, she must face the secrets of the psychiatric hospital, but the biggest fight is against her own mind.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Narrative Story: Delve into a dark and gritty story with mechanics inspired by survival horror games from the ps2 era.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cooperative Campaign: Play the story alone or with a friend in split screen.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Transversality: Climb through the scenarios to reach objectives and solve puzzles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hide or Fight: Go unnoticed without alerting enemies or use the different melee and fire weapons to finish them off.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inventory System: Collect items, manage your resources and combine them to solve puzzles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1990060/extras/be79f42f174dbb9db4ed340dba1cb9d1.poster.avif?t=1748622577\" width=720 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1990060/extras/be79f42f174dbb9db4ed340dba1cb9d1.webm?t=1748622577\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1990060/extras/be79f42f174dbb9db4ed340dba1cb9d1.mp4?t=1748622577\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Note: Co-op mode can only be played with joysticks, not mouse and keyboard, so you'll need two controllers to play properly.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Claudia, a woman who has lost her job as a reporter, decides to go to investigate the psychiatric hospital \"Milagros\" which keeps a story as secret as it is macabre. During this journey she meets people who have the same intentions and others who will get in the way.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With the help of her new companions, she must face the secrets of the psychiatric hospital, but the biggest fight is against her own mind.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Narrative Story: Delve into a dark and gritty story with mechanics inspired by survival horror games from the ps2 era.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cooperative Campaign: Play the story alone or with a friend in split screen.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Transversality: Climb through the scenarios to reach objectives and solve puzzles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hide or Fight: Go unnoticed without alerting enemies or use the different melee and fire weapons to finish them off.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inventory System: Collect items, manage your resources and combine them to solve puzzles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1990060/extras/be79f42f174dbb9db4ed340dba1cb9d1.poster.avif?t=1748622577\" width=720 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1990060/extras/be79f42f174dbb9db4ed340dba1cb9d1.webm?t=1748622577\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1990060/extras/be79f42f174dbb9db4ed340dba1cb9d1.mp4?t=1748622577\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Note: Co-op mode can only be played with joysticks, not mouse and keyboard, so you'll need two controllers to play properly.</p>",
